Products.Name: Garmin T2875.62 Tacx NEO 2T Smart Trainer - Black

Properties.Name: LongDescription
Properties.Value:
With an improved design and revamped components, the Garmin T2875.62 NEO 2T Smart trainer provides a more immersive experience, wider pedal stroke analysis compatibility and more. Redesigned magnets have significantly improved the stillness of NEO 2T Smart. Internal air displacement and vibrations are reduced, resulting in a remarkably silent trainer. NEO 2T Smart reacts instantly to speed or incline changes and allows for movement to the left and right while cycling, following the natural course of your body. When connected to an external power source, descent simulation accurately simulates a downhill drive. NEO 2T Smart features a new motor design that delivers more power at low speeds, resulting in a highly improved ride feel during a climb or acceleration. 32 integrated neodymium magnets allow for a high brake force and high power levels. NEO 2T Smart ensures maximum stability, even during explosive sprints, up to 2,200 watts.
